        <p>If we have reason to believe, in our sole discretion, you are not using NeoScaffold in accordance with the terms of this agreement, then we may take any technical or legal steps to prevent you (or any other users thereafter) from accessing our services, and/or make amends for anything resulting from such actions directly or indirectly.</p>
        <h2 id="4policyenforcement">4. Policy Enforcement</h2>
        <p>When an issue arises regarding the use of NeoScaffold or some other policy infringement occurs, we may consider what is best for NeoScaffold and our users in applying our policies. We may choose to be more lenient with policy enforcement in an effort to do the right thing for NeoScaffold and its users.</p>
        <h2 id="5fees">5. Fees</h2>
        <p>There are fees for some uses of NeoScaffold. The fees we charge are prominently listed on NeoScaffold. We may change some of the fees by posting the changes on NeoScaffold 14 days in advance, but without notice for promotions or discounts that result in the reduction of fees. Fees are charged to your account that must have a payment method on file when accessing uses of NeoScaffold that involve fees. You must also pay all fees and applicable taxes associated with NeoScaffold by the payment due date. If your payment method fails or your account is past due, we may collect amounts owed by charging other payment methods on file with us, and retain collection agencies and legal counsel. You will also be subject to late fees. No fees on NeoScaffold purchase exclusive rights to workflow exposure on NeoScaffold.</p>
        <h2 id="6membership">6. Membership</h2>
        <p>If you purchase any NeoScaffold membership, your membership will continue month-to-month and automatically renew until terminated. In order to use NeoScaffold, you must have internet access, a capable device, a valid payment method, and an account registered to an eligible user. We may offer many different membership plans, including special promotional plans or memberships offered by third parties in conjunction with the provision of their own products or services. We are not responsible for the aforementioned 3rd party products or services and they may have differing limitations, which are disclosed at sign up and updated if they change. We reserve the right to change our membership plans or adjust pricing in any way or time as we may determine in our sole and absolute discretion. We will post any changes to memberships at least 14 days in advance. The membership fees, and any other charges you may incur while you have a membership will be charged on a monthly basis to your payment method on the first day of each month. You can cancel your membership(s) at any time, and you will continue to have access to NeoScaffold memberships and its benefits at least to the end of the billing period.</p>
        <h2 id="7aboutrefunds">7. About Refunds</h2>
        <p>Payments for fees or charges are nonrefundable and there are no refunds or credits for partially used membership periods. At any time, and for any reason, we may provide a refund, discount, or other consideration to users ("credits"). The amount and form of such credits, and the decision to provide them, are at our sole discretion. The provision of credits in one instance doesn't entitle you to credits for similar instances, nor does it obligate us to provide any credits in the future.</p>
